# Placeholder so wwwroot/ exists for ASP.NET Core's StaticFiles middleware.
#
# In production, `make up` (root Makefile) copies the built Vite SPA from
# `frontend/dist/` into this directory before publishing the backend, so
# the API process serves both the JSON API at /api/* and the SPA on every
# other path.
#
# In Development this directory normally stays empty — the SPA is served
# by `vite dev` on :5173 with /api proxied to the backend on :5000.
